{"id":232663160,"title":"美國騎重機分享","content":"快畢業了，想要試試不同的，所以就去學騎重機了\n\n在美國（加州）考重機駕照蠻簡單的，只要上一個motorcycle safety course + DMV 筆試 就可以拿到駕照， 一個禮拜搞定\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZO.jpg\n⬆️我在駕訓班練的車，居然是野狼？？\n\n剛好我朋友要賣忍300，就跟他買了，查了一下覺得美國車價真的比台灣親民很多\nhttps://i.imgur.com/4OWcSbj.jpg\n\n因為美國可以騎上高速公路，所以我就買了半套全裝\nhttps://i.imgur.com/1NEKm8W.jpg\n目前騎了快三個禮拜，還是有點怕，尤其是騎在高速公路上的時候，因為周圍的車都快我好多😂\n\n聖誕節回台灣也打算考個機車駕照，希望以後在台灣也能騎","excerpt":"快畢業了，想要試試不同的，所以就去學騎重機了，在美國（加州）考重機駕照蠻簡單的，只要上一個motorcycle safety course + DMV 筆試 就可以拿到駕照， 一個禮拜搞定，⬆️我在駕","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2cffc289-d332-4d4e-95a7-cae58a1778aa","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-10T17:38:58.648Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T17:38:58.648Z","commentCount":38,"likeCount":199,"tags":[],"topics":["重機","美國","檔車","新手","心得"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"重機","forumAlias":"heavy_motorcycle","school":"加州大學聖地亞哥分校","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":199}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZO.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/4OWcSbj.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/1NEKm8W.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"944767aa-44d0-40ef-be40-afe415c75031","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZOl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZOl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZOl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T17:38:58.648Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T17:38:58.648Z"},{"id":"944767aa-44d0-40ef-be40-afe415c75031","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZO.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/bgFcZZO","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bgFcZZOl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T17:38:58.648Z","updatedAt":"2019-1